Description: Functions for computing a standardized moderation
             effect and forming its confidence interval by
             nonparametric bootstrapping correctly. Supports
             outputs from 'stats::lm()' and 'lavaan::lavaan()'.
URL: https://sfcheung.github.io/stdmod/
